F-1.1@Now, let’s look at VHF/HF communications.
|
F-1.2@You tune VHF and HF radios with radio tuning panels.
|
F-1.3@The radio tuning panels are on the aft electronic panel.
|
F-1.4@The panels are identical, independent, and may be used at the same time.
|
