|
F-2.2@You use these knobs to set the frequencies.
|
F-2.3@You use the transfer switch to select the active frequency.
|
F-2.4@The offside tuning light illuminates whenever a different radio is selected for tuning.
|
F-3.1@Tune VHF 1 to frequency 121.900 from RTP 2.
|
F-3.2@Select VHF 2 on RTP 2.
|
